{"id":1020464595,"lang":"csharp","lang_name":"C#","time":"4 months, 1 week","timestamp":1691951704,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"1304 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1020464595/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"3Sum","memory":"127.7 MB","code":"public class Solution {\n    \n    public IList<IList<int>> ThreeSum(int[] nums) {\n        IList<IList<int>> ans = new List<IList<int>>();\n        var set = new HashSet<int>();\n        var tempSet = new HashSet<string>();\n        for(var i = 0; i < nums.Length; i++){\n            for (var j=i+1; j< nums.Length; j++){\n                var req = -(nums[i] + nums[j]);\n                if(set.Contains(req)){\n                    var triplet = new List<int>(){nums[i], nums[j], req};\n                    triplet.Sort();\n                    var tripletString = string.Join(\",\", triplet);\n                    if(tempSet.Add(tripletString)){\n                        ans.Add(triplet);\n                    }\n                }\n                else{\n                    set.Add(nums[j]);\n                }\n            }\n            set.Clear();\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"3sum","has_notes":true,"flag_type":1}
